name: Supermodel Makeover by Lauren Luke
overview: 10 contest modes to complete - including Boho Babe, Prom style, Egyptian Goddess, Retro Style, Beach Style, Halloween Fancy Dress, Disco Star plus many more! Over 250 fashion items! EXCLUSIVE unlockable Lauren Luke make-up tutorials 2 modes of play - play in Contest Mode or get creative with your look in Freestyle mode 9 unlockable fashion themed mini-games Save your best looks in your model portfolio to share with your friends
